# Input

```grit
`console.$method('$message');` => `console.warn('$message');` where {
  any {

  $message <: r"Hello, .*!",     $method <: `log` }
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`console.$method('$message');` => `console.warn('$message');` where {
	any { $message <: r"Hello, .*!", $method <: `log` }
}

```
